{"tid":663552,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"窮人眼中的有錢人","createTime":"2018-05-13T11:34:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T03:13:25.000Z","uid":42188,"like":63,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1358ec5b543946c7579e355f60bb2ffd0c0d97bb","tid":663552,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T11:34:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 覺得有錢人晚晚都工作到好夜，d仔女會怪父母冇時間理佢地</span><br />\n<br />\n事實係你d窮仔女既怨氣仲大，例如冇錢同同學去玩/無錢買對波鞋/etc...<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2. 覺得有錢人總係百病纏身，再覺得雖然自己窮，但身體健康，再推論「再多錢都買唔到健康」</span><br />\n<br />\n事實係窮人有病去排公立，排排下已經病死既例子大有人在。有錢人病，起碼可以即刻睇私家，存活率大大提高<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3. 覺得有錢人d仔女全部都各懷鬼胎，等兩老一死就點爭身家</span><br />\n<br />\n事實呢啲只係電視劇既橋段，現實生活中，只佔少數。更重要既係，你都冇身家留俾d窮仔女，d仔女爭條毛?"},{"pid":"aa2c0d662d3c4e5d013ee3ea8a78f6a7bb57f360","tid":663552,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T11:51:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e0a63f794a8f112e6464a73377cdbf1a61203a4","tid":663552,"uid":170202,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T11:58:47.000Z","msg":"覺得有錢人仔女不成器，窮人仔女刻苦好學。"},{"pid":"5c01fd0f41975847bd8e8defed2a608a77d23c1a","tid":663552,"uid":58201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T12:05:21.000Z","msg":"結論 睇得太多tvb"},{"pid":"0e23d8d311589487af833add18d18e29e901763e","tid":663552,"uid":44391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T12:13:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"60c761799ba8bce526c34968a5edab0eb73b6333","tid":663552,"uid":67551,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"6e0a63f794a8f112e6464a73377cdbf1a61203a4","tid":663552,"uid":170202,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T11:58:47.000Z","msg":"覺得有錢人仔女不成器，窮人仔女刻苦好學。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T12:15:05.000Z","msg":"實情有錢人資源充足，接受更高等嘅師資同教育，出一分力好過窮撚溫一日<br />\n<br />\n窮撚冇咩錢，下下一試定生死<br />\n有錢人唔得就慢慢來，再試試<br />\n再唔得去外國讀cc入名校<br />\ngap year, working holiday隨便玩<br />\n稍為無大志嘅喺外國定居都已經過緊窮撚憧憬嘅退休生活"},{"pid":"ba8ff206342b3cd8f1c5e87b0e28f2d23d21a31d","tid":663552,"uid":54777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T12:25:04.000Z","msg":"第一點唔係調翻轉咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237c04a89d3d6e4b56d6a60c9489d274f10c49b0","tid":663552,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T14:52:18.000Z","msg":"覺得有錢人會睇TVB 明珠台<br />\n窮人會睇TVB 翡翠台<br />\n<br />\n事實系無論有錢or窮人<br />\n一出世間醫院部電視機都長開播住TVB<br />\n出街食間間茶餐廳部部電視機都長開播住TVB<br />\n去急症室/診所部電視機都長開播住TVB<br />\n屋企樓下電梯大堂部電視機都長開播住TVB"},{"pid":"7352ba1c26b5304005308743503a72acdc515636","tid":663552,"uid":25221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T15:36:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a2a1dc8ac1e8288e6181345bed87e914798898ac","tid":663552,"uid":3549,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T17:20:42.000Z","msg":"最撚ON9係覺得有錢人太有錢會唔開心"},{"pid":"ae95052560e3217a75d4ac2e6f389a3532115e3a","tid":663552,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T02:14:57.000Z","msg":"最後嗰段真係估你唔到"},{"pid":"6d3ad114d1a735ccb59a8992513876c19f6b6a40","tid":663552,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2a1dc8ac1e8288e6181345bed87e914798898ac","tid":663552,"uid":3549,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T17:20:42.000Z","msg":"最撚ON9係覺得有錢人太有錢會唔開心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T03:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa2d10f88bcc49eaf03b70cf6c4706873e1bdc2f","tid":663552,"uid":145589,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T04:41:50.000Z","msg":"如果窮人知有錢人生活咁好 <br />\n佢地攞咩麻醉自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n梗係呃自己「富不過三代」啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事實係有錢家族世世代代都有錢<br />\n因為佢地已經掌控左知識同資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97394336a0a8816f5a2793c75af48df7437c9f5b","tid":663552,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T04:50:25.000Z","msg":"有價值嘅野就有人要搶架啦，邊分有冇錢人。大至鷹君集團，細至快餐店個名都可以爭埋一份"},{"pid":"885e41340c4f4810a32d143fc0c21af43e5228aa","tid":663552,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T03:13:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}